Package: minTX
Type: Package
Title: Minimize the Number of Transactions between Counterparties Needed to
    Settle Debts
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Miguel Biron Lattes
Maintainer: Miguel Biron Lattes <miguelbl9@gmail.com>
Description: The purpose of this package is to solve the problem of minimizing
    the number of transactions between counterparties that have outstanding
    debts between them. We use a Linear Programming formulation to tackle it.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
